<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224270>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Ophidiotrichus exastus Higgins, adult female, dorsal aspect, legs and rostral setae not illustrated. Scale bar = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/224270/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224268>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8 A, B. Lateral aspect of podosoma of adult female, legs and notogaster removed: A, Joelia appalachia sp. nov., with arrow to lateral indentation on bothridium. B, Ophidiotrichus exastus Higgins, with arrow to ventral indentation in area of connection of pedotectum I to body wall. Scale bars = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/224268/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224263>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ferolocella tessalata (Berlese), adult female, dorsal aspect, legs not illustrated, with arrow to squared base of interlamellar pocket. Scale bar = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/224263/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224271>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Ophidiotrichus exastus Higgins, adult female, ventral aspect, legs and rostral setae not illustrated, with arrow to the tache pectorale. Scale bar = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/224271/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224272>
    dc:description "FIGURE 12 A – D. Ophidiotrichus exastus Higgins, differential interference contrast microscope images of adults: A, ventral region anterior to middle of genital plate, with arrow to tache pectorale; B, detail of lateral of coxisternum in region of pedotectum II (PdII), with arrow to dens at tip of pteromorph folded over coxisternum; custodium and seta 4 c visible beneath; C, detail of tache pectoral e; D, detail of striae on anterior and lateral of coxisternum, tache pectoral e indicated with arrow. Scale bars: A – D = 25 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/224272/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

